# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Client environment variables (Vite)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy this file to .env.local for local overrides.
# In Catalyst Slate, set these as deployment environment variables.
#
# VITE_API_BASE
#   Full base URL of the Catalyst Advanced I/O function.
#   Required when the SPA is hosted on Catalyst Slate (*.onslate.in),
#   because the function lives on a different origin (*.catalystserverless.com).
#
#   Format:  https://<project-domain>.catalystserverless.com/server/ds-analyzer
#   Example: https://creator-ds-analyser-123456789.catalystserverless.com/server/ds-analyzer
#
#   Leave empty (or unset) for local development — the Vite dev-server
#   proxy forwards /api and /health to http://localhost:3001 automatically.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
VITE_API_BASE=
